{"id":"61b71613-8e78-4c0e-9f3c-e1d2486b3b27","name":"Welcome to Hell's dirtiest, deadliest tournament","description":"<p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0ecoWLXYvLB0Q2yhyKg6O.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>The sky is the color of a fresh bruise. The ground is obsidian and bone. Rivers of molten shadow carve through the landscape like veins pumping liquid lust. The air smells of ash, ambition, and the faint, sweet tang of arousal.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>Once every five centuries, the 116 demon houses set aside their petty wars for something far more dangerous.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>The Septem Peccata Crucible.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>Seven phases. Seven sins. Seven chances to rise — or be crushed beneath the heels of those who climb over your broken body.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>And somewhere in the crowd, standing on black glass that reflects your own hungry eyes back at you, is you.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>Champion. Summoned creature. Rogue anomaly. Something else entirely.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>Your role is undefined. Your body is yours. Your desires are yours.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>The tournament does not care what you are. Only what you can do.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>But Hell? Hell is watching.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 73, 0);\"><strong>And Hell is always, always hungry.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 255, 0);\"><strong>---</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Short Version (Because You Want to Get to the Fucking)</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 255, 0);\"><strong>You are in Hell. There are 116 demon houses. They rank from 1 (basically gods) to 116 (basically fucked). Every 500 years, they hold a tournament called the Septem Peccata Crucible. Seven phases. Seven sins. Seven chances to rise.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/wQkf52TfwHz088YiwG_Rk.webp\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 255, 0);\"><strong>If you win, your house ascends. If you lose, your house descends — sometimes into total absorption.</stron","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"tZ5_HqnQLDCx0YUmy6ETW.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🪢 Scenario","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🌗 Switch"],"chats":766,"messages":21366,"created_at":"2026-05-04T11:49:30.505736+00:00"}